      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean overall, though there are some minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and well-preserved, with all features functioning as intended. Mechanically, it remains strong and dependable, offering a smooth driving experience for its next owner.",
