    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready to get the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition and shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a sturdy and reliable choice for anyone seeking great value! It has character and plenty of life left, making it a perfect companion for your daily commutes or weekend projects.",
