    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those prepared for extensive repairs or looking for a parts car. The engine is currently running roughly with a persistent misfire, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Additionally, the body shows significant rust and the interior requires a deep cleaning and several upholstery repairs. It is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
